name: Big Bang EP
description:
The debut EP from glam-pop-panda-rock quartet the Maybenauts featuring five original tracks.

This EP will not be officially released until May 21, but you will receive your copy EARLY because we love you.

1. Girlfight
2. My Head Is A Bomb
3. You Are Here
4. Not Aware
5. Blue Line

name: Maybefits tee
description:
These tees are a delightful play on everyone's favourite horror punk band. Everyone loves a skull panda!

Tees are a white silkscreen on a black Tultex 100% ringspun cotton tee, available in women's and men's sizes.

Women's sizing chart is here: http://secure.bluecollardistro.com/sizing/tultex_girls/
Men's sizing chart is here: http://secure.bluecollardistro.com/sizing/tultex/

If your size is SOLD OUT, check back soon!  We are having more printed!!  :)

name: Collect-All-Four 1" Buttons!
description:
Wear your Maybenauts on your sleeve!

You'll get one of each 1" Maybenauts button: Leilaninaut, the Space Panda, Emilynaut, and Ellienaut.

name: Donate to the Maybenauts
description: Love us? We love you too! Unfortunately, we're broke and this making-music business can get quite costly. Donations can be made in increments of $10.00. You will be able to adjust the quantity (and thus the size of your donation) after clicking the "add to cart" button. For your donation you will receive: 1) a warm fuzzy feeling, 2) our unconditional love/undying gratitude, and 3) a limited edition, numbered copy of our EP Big Bang autographed by all four members of the Maybenauts. Donation Gratitude Reward #3 is for a limited time only - we've only numbered the first 100 copies of the CD and have already gone through #32! Requests for a specific number will be honoured based on availability, but we can't make any promises. Limit 1 CD per donor, regardless of donation size (if you really want more copies, you can buy them here). If you really really REALLY must have an extra signed/numbered copy for your uncle's wife's dog breeder's daughter, send us an e-mail and we can probably work something out. :) THANK YOU! Your donation means the Maybenauts can keep Maybenautting.
